{"tid":346603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"據報特朗普推遲宣布調查中國的貿易行為","createTime":"2017-08-04T05:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T07:10:26.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59b826523d3502615cc158c60cefa0d4a509d32d","tid":346603,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"據報特朗普推遲宣布調查中國的貿易行為<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普據報推遲宣布調查中國的貿易行為。  美國財經頻道CNBC引述消息指，特朗普原訂星期五會公開批評中國，有侵權和不公平貿易行為，並會簽署總統備忘錄，要求貿易代表萊特希澤開始調查相關事宜，但有關活動將會推遲，未知道原因，亦沒有設定何日再宣布。  《路透》引述外交消息指，美國可能與中國，就在聯合國層面加強制裁北韓達成協議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/finance/5983c4756db28cb0029f574a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Ffinance%2F5983c4756db28cb0029f574a&d=dqDVpvofywcWVKxrf4%2Bf2jCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=6ce9c971\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/finance/5983c4756db28cb0029f574a</a>"},{"pid":"1ea5799db205c41c441a795fbdaf6d20a7696aeb","tid":346603,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"又放生支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943d523d25e07f4407e1ed5891e87a7d120c8100","tid":346603,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:54:52.000Z","msg":"全盛時期侵侵撚連登仔幾多次? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047fe8c10b0b00eaf7d1beb2676f5621452ae7fb","tid":346603,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"點解cctvb news咁撚鐘意據報?"},{"pid":"49573c9b12f010f8da3987e55dee6b0d3a47e609","tid":346603,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全盛時期侵侵撚連登仔幾多次? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n交換條件，攪金仔就唔攪佢"},{"pid":"f745a2f8321ebd5b0b940acc6d66407250be7ad7","tid":346603,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2